ivardefs.name: member
ivardefs.desc: The specific person or organization who is participating/expected to participate in the care team.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: Indicates when the specific member or organization did (or is intended to) come into effect and end.

ivardefs.name: role
ivardefs.desc: Indicates specific responsibility of an individual within the care team, such as "Primary care physician", "Trained social worker counselor", "Caregiver", etc.

properties.desc: Identifies all people and organizations who are expected to be involved in the care team.
